data.description: Charming and affordable! Outside has shade with pecan trees, plenty of fenced room in the yard for entertaining under the covered patio, or cook outs on the concrete area. Storage building in the backyard stays and plenty of room to play outside. Inside boasts stainless appliances, hardwood floors, and ample storage in closets and cabinets. Refrigerator in kitchen stays. Utility room in garage. Multiple windows to allow natural light. Breakfast bar and stand alone pantry in kitchen. Kitchen renovated in 2010. New roof in 2014. Don't miss your chance to own such a great home at such an affordable price, WITH all of the extras!
